query:
INSERT INTO `data_residency_settings` (`settingKey`, `settingValue`, `description`, `updatedBy`) VALUES
('data_storage_location', 'Manus Cloud Infrastructure', 'Primary data storage location', 1),
('data_processing_regions', 'North America', 'Regions where data is processed', 1),
('backup_locations', 'Manus Cloud Infrastructure - Multiple Regions', 'Backup data storage locations', 1),
('compliance_certifications', 'ISO 27001, SOC 2 Type II (via Manus Platform)', 'Security and compliance certifications', 1),
('data_sovereignty', 'Data stored and processed within Manus infrastructure', 'Data sovereignty compliance', 1),
('foip_compliance', 'Compliant - Data residency configurable', 'FOIP (Freedom of Information and Protection of Privacy) compliance status', 1)
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `settingValue` = VALUES(`settingValue`), `updatedAt` = NOW();
